    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator with adaptive smoothing based on input rate of change. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Automatically adjusts smoothing based on how fast the input is changing. Uses fixed time base from Heartbeat for consistent behavior.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Motor</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base motor class (must implement Go(signed short)) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kMinTimeConstantMs</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Minimum time constant (fast response). Default: 10ms </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kMaxTimeConstantMs</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Maximum time constant (heavy smoothing). Default: 150ms </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
